         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botanic Garden, ¶ 7 August 1872. ¶  ¶ I have sent you, noble friend, a  ¶ Cycas ¶  trunk (of  ¶ Cycas angulata ¶ ), many years old, in living state, by the ship  ¶ Yorkshire ¶ , ¶  which wil...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">72.08.07a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne im bot Garten</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">7/8/72.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit dem Schiffe Yorkshire, edler Freund, habe ich Ihnen einen vieljährigen Cycas Stamm (ein <name key="Cycas%20angulata">Cycas angulata</name>) im lebenden Zustand gesandt, der sich wohl ebenso leicht wieder belauben wird, als es die alten Stämme von <name key="Encephalartos">Encephalartos</name> aus Natal u dem Kafferland thun, wenn man sie unter Glass in Bodenwärme bringt.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich würde rathen, den Stamm erst wohl durchzuräuchern, ehe er ins Treibhaus kommt, um die Larva u Ova von Bohrkäfern oder andern Insekten zu zerstören.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Meine Agenten, Mess Blackith &amp; Co sind beauftragt Ihnen den Stamm <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">kostenfrei</hi>
               </seg> zuzusenden.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit Ihrem ausgezeichneten Freunde dem Chev. Dr Christophersen habe ich vielfach verkehrt.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit ehrender Ergebenheit</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Im Falle zeitigen Frostes haben Sie vielleicht Gelegenheit einen Freund in London zu bitten, den Stamm für Sie im Treibhaus bis zum Frühjahr u überwintern.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne Botanic Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7 August 1872.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have sent you, noble friend, a <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Cycas</seg> trunk (of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Cycas%20angulata">Cycas angulata</name>
               </seg>), many years old, in living state, by the ship <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Yorkshire</seg>,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Yorkshire</seg> sailed for London on 8 August 1872 (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>, 9 August 1872, p. 4).</p>
               </note> which will probably grow fronds again just as easily as the old trunks of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Encephalartos">Encephalartos</name>
               </seg> from Natal and Kaffirland, when they are brought under glass and given bottom heat.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I would advise to smoke the trunk well before placing it in the glasshouse, to destroy any larvae and eggs of boring beetles or other insects.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My agents, Mess Blackith &amp; Co, have been instructed to send you the trunk <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">free of charge</hi>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have met frequently with your excellent friend Chevalier Dr Christophersen.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Wilhelm Christopher Christophersen (1832-1913), while Consul for Norway and Sweden in Buenos Aires, visited Vic and SA during 1872-3 (see, for example, <seg style="font-style: italic; ">South Australian register,</seg> 24 September 1872, p. 5, and <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg>, 18 July 1873, p. 2).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With respectful devotion</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">In case of early frost you may perhaps have the opportunity to ask a friend in London to winter the trunk for you in his glasshouse until spring.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Cycas%20angulata">Cycas angulata</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Encephalartos">Encephalartos</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
